Class ArcImsWizardData

java.lang.Object
  es.prodevelop.cit.gvsig.arcims.fmap.datasource.ArcImsWizardData

public class ArcImsWizardData
extends java.lang.Object

This class implements a data source object, owned by the ArcImsWizard object. It will create the ArcIMS layer and load some basic data.
